17
00:03:46,811 --> 00:03:48,438
Penuh tekad.

18
00:03:51,649 --> 00:03:54,402
- Masih belum ada?
- Tak ada tanda apa pun.

19
00:03:54,402 --> 00:03:57,321
- Sudah berapa lama dia pergi?
- Hampir dua jam.

20
00:04:00,283 --> 00:04:02,160
Akankah mereka melawan, Pak?

21
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,703
Kita akan segera tahu.

22
00:04:03,703 --> 00:04:06,330
Prajurit, pindahkan
katapel itu ke depan.

23
00:04:06,330 --> 00:04:08,666
- Terlalu jauh.
- Sudah pas.

24
00:04:10,334 --> 00:04:13,755
- Bahaya untuk kavaleri...
- Bisa diterima. Ya?

25
00:04:23,431 --> 00:04:24,515
Mereka menolak.

26
00:04:50,458 --> 00:04:53,002
Semua harus tahu
saat mereka takluk.

27
00:05:03,471 --> 00:05:05,264
Kau mau takluk, Quintus?

28
00:05:06,182 --> 00:05:07,975
Apa aku mau takluk?

29
00:05:24,242 --> 00:05:26,119
- Kekuatan dan kehormatan.
- Kekuatan dan kehormatan.

30
00:05:26,119 --> 00:05:27,579
Kekuatan dan kehormatan.

31
00:05:32,583 --> 00:05:35,711
Saat kuberi sinyal,
mulai serangan..

32
00:05:58,442 --> 00:05:59,944
Isi katapel tempur.

33
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:02,780
Infanteri, bersiap maju.

34
00:06:04,282 --> 00:06:06,784
- Pemanah siap.
- Pemanah!

35
00:06:06,784 --> 00:06:08,244
- Siap!
- Siap!

36
00:06:32,018 --> 00:06:33,477
Saudaraku!

37
00:06:33,477 --> 00:06:35,313
Maximus! Maximus!

38
00:06:36,772 --> 00:06:40,860
Tiga minggu lagi, aku
akan memanen tanamanku.

39
00:06:40,985 --> 00:06:45,406
Bayangkan di mana
kalian, dan itu akan terjadi.

40
00:06:46,115 --> 00:06:49,535
Tahan barisan! Tetap bersamaku!

41
00:06:49,535 --> 00:06:52,288
Jika kalian merasa sendirian,

42
00:06:52,288 --> 00:06:55,291
berkuda di padang rumput
diterpa sinar mentari,

43
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:58,669
jangan cemas.

44
00:06:59,503 --> 00:07:03,132
Karena kalian ada di
Elysium, dan kalian sudah mati!

45
00:07:05,301 --> 00:07:06,969
Saudaraku,

46
00:07:08,346 --> 00:07:10,181
perbuatan kita semasa hidup

47
00:07:11,265 --> 00:07:12,934
bergema selamanya.

48
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,693
Tarik!

49
00:07:38,334 --> 00:07:40,336
Katapel siap, Pak!

50
00:07:51,097 --> 00:07:53,391
Pemanah, nyalakan!

51
00:07:53,641 --> 00:07:56,268
- Nyalakan!
- Nyalakan!

52
00:08:02,149 --> 00:08:04,819
Pemanah, tarik busur!

53
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,657
Lontarkan!

54
00:08:38,769 --> 00:08:40,771
Semua, siap!

55
00:08:46,610 --> 00:08:48,529
Tahan barisan!

56
