Hidup! Hidup!

885
01:40:08,440 --> 01:40:10,270
Hidup! Hidup!

886
01:40:10,270 --> 01:40:12,000
Hidup! Hidup!

887
01:40:12,000 --> 01:40:13,830
Hidup! Hidup!

888
01:40:13,830 --> 01:40:16,330
Hidup! Hidup! Hidup!

889
01:40:49,670 --> 01:40:52,422
Turunkan senjata!

890
01:41:36,699 --> 01:41:46,900
Maximus! Maximus! Maximus!

891
01:41:46,932 --> 01:42:02,211
Maximus! Maximus! Maximus!

892
01:42:37,402 --> 01:42:38,570
Ayah.

893
01:43:52,936 --> 01:43:54,813
Kenapa dia masih hidup?

894
01:43:56,064 --> 01:43:57,566
Aku tak tahu.

895
01:43:58,066 --> 01:43:59,651
Dia seharusnya mati.

896
01:44:00,485 --> 01:44:01,903
Itu membuatku kesal.

897
01:44:03,655 --> 01:44:05,449
Aku sangat kesal.

898
01:44:16,668 --> 01:44:18,587
Itu harus kulakukan.

899
01:44:19,337 --> 01:44:23,467
Jika keinginan Ayah terwujud,
kekaisaran akan hancur.

900
01:44:23,467 --> 01:44:25,135
Kau paham?

901
01:44:25,510 --> 01:44:26,678
Ya.

902
01:44:31,475 --> 01:44:34,686
Apa yang kau rasakan
saat melihatnya?

903
01:44:36,813 --> 01:44:38,440
Tak ada rasa.

904
01:44:40,400 --> 01:44:42,944
Dia sangat menyakitimu, bukan?

905
01:44:43,987 --> 01:44:46,198
Tak lebih dari aku menyakitinya.

906
01:44:50,702 --> 01:44:52,996
Mereka membohongiku.

907
01:44:54,623 --> 01:44:56,708
Katanya dia sudah mati.

908
01:44:58,710 --> 01:45:01,379
Berarti mereka
tak menghormatiku.

909
01:45:01,379 --> 01:45:04,716
Jika begitu, bagaimana
bisa mencintaiku?

910
01:45:06,051 --> 01:45:08,512
Jika begitu, tunjukkan legiun

911
01:45:08,512 --> 01:45:11,598
pengkhianatan takkan dibiarkan.

912
01:45:12,432 --> 01:45:13,892
Kakakku yang malang.

913
01:45:14,309 --> 01:45:16,770
Aku tak ingin jadi musuhmu.

914
01:45:17,979 --> 01:45:19,731
Apa tindakanmu?

915
01:45:32,702 --> 01:45:34,037
Kemari.

916
01:46:09,406 --> 01:46:12,951
Janda kaya membayar mahal
untuk dipuaskan sang juara.

917
01:46:12,951 --> 01:46:15,453
Aku tahu dia akan
kirim pembunuh.

918
01:46:15,954 --> 01:46:18,694
Tak kusangka adikmu
kirim yang terbaik.

919
01:46:20,208 --> 01:46:22,294
Maximus, dia tak tahu.

920
01:46:23,253 --> 01:46:26,464
Keluargaku dibakar dan
disalib saat mereka masih hidup.

921
01:46:26,464 --> 01:46:29,009
- Aku tak tahu...
- Jangan bohong!

922
01:46:35,473 --> 01:46:37,309
Aku menangisi mereka.

923
01:46:37,309 --> 01:46:41,229
